    "And many organisations don't stop and think.",
    "They just do, and as a result we have a lot of biased AI and a lot of problems.",
    "So, I think the concept of having an AI ethics committee can be very, very valuable and we should actually move that from the university to the more corporate world as well.\"",
    "(R2).The importance of fine-grained contextual factors, and not merely relying on generic procedural ethics, was also noted.",
